ady</strong>.</p>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center">Filtered theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://themetrust.com/themes/filtered/"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493" src="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/filtered.png" alt="ekho" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>A stylish and responsive portfolio theme.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themetrust.com/themes/filtered/" target="_blank">Download Filtered theme</a></div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center">X-the theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/x-the-theme/5871901"><img src="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/x.png" alt="ekho" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Achieve virtually any look and layout from within the one and only X WordPress Theme. Stacks allow you to choose from multiple, completely unique designs with just the click of a mouse, and there are currently four Stacks to choose from (with more in development).</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/x-the-theme/5871901">Purchase X theme</a></div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center">rtMedia plugin</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/buddypress-media/"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493" src="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/rtmedia.png" alt="ekho" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Add albums, photo, audio/video encoding, privacy, sharing, front-end uploads &#038; more. All this works on mobile/tablets devices.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/buddypress-media/">Download rtMedia plugin</a></div>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=